Package com.hemebiotech.analytics

package com.hemebiotech.analytics
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    ISymptomCounter
    An interface to count unique symptoms from a text file.
    ISymptomReader
    An interface to read unique symptoms from a text file.
    ISymptomWriter
    This Interface writes the content of a ISymptomCounter Object to a file
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    AnalyticsCounter
    Creates an analytics object used to list and count distinct lines contained in a text file.
    It will not count blank lines.
    CountDataFromFile
    Creates an object that contains a text source file, a list of its unique distinguished lines, and a Map of these lines and their number occurrences in the source file.
    ExtractLinesFromFile
    Class that implements the interface ISymptoms reader and that defines methods to read and extract the symptoms of a file line by line.
    Main
    This is the main program that counts symptoms in a text file and write them in an output file
    WriteMapStringIntegerToFile
    Create an object that will write the content of a map into a file
